meta.description:
Footage circulating on social media shows a pharmacist unboxing a sealed Johnson & Johnson Covid vaccine — only to find the package insert is completely blank. 

Read and share the bombshell study from UT researchers that warns about the dangers of Covid vaccines below: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3335060/pdf/pone.0035421.pdf

title: Pharmacist Shows Blank COVID 19 Vaccine Insert
